OL,3,CCharity football match to highlight
OL,4,Chelp available for gambling addition
OL,6,FA day ahead of the start of the
OL,7,FPremiere League season, a special
OL,8,Ffootball match has been held to raise
OL,9,Fawareness of the serious harms of
OL,10,Fgambling addiction throughout Ireland.
OL,12,FIt's also hoped that taking the
OL,13,FGambling with Lives campaign to the
OL,14,Ffootball pitch at Harland and Wolff
OL,15,FWelders stadium that it will encourage
OL,16,Fother sports clubs to take the issue
OL,17,Fseriously and sign up to prevention
OL,18,Fprogrammes.
OL,20,FBetting on football is one form of
OL,21,Fgambling addition.
