OL,6,FAnd the friendly match had a serious
OL,7,Fgoal - to raise awareness of the
OL,8,Fdamaging effects of gambling in any
OL,9,Fform.
OL,11,FSadie and Pete Keogh's son Lewis took
OL,12,Fhis own life in 2013 after his
OL,13,Fgambling got out of control. Now they
OL,14,Fspend their lives helping others to
OL,15,Fconfront their addition.
OL,17,FSadie said: "He left a note that read,
OL,18,F'Please forgive me but every day is a
OL,19,Fnightmare. All I need is a bit of
OL,20,Fpeace. Please understand that
OL,21,Faddiction is cruel'".
