OL,6,FIt's estimated that 2.3 percent of
OL,7,Fpeople in Northern Ireland suffer with
OL,8,Fproblem gambling.
OL,10,FOn the island of Ireland, the figure
OL,11,Fis one in thirty people.
OL,13,FSinn Fein's Philip McGuigan is
OL,14,Frecovering from a gambling addiction.
OL,15,FHe is using his role as a politician
OL,16,Fto help bring about the change of law
OL,17,Fwith regard to the Gambling Industry.
