OL,6,FHe said: "It is vitally important that
OL,7,Fif there are people listening who are
OL,8,Fsuffering from addiction, that they
OL,9,Fknow that there is an opportunity to
OL,10,Frecover and live a very fulfilling
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,F"Obviously I have a certain amount of
OL,14,Fresponsibility in that at Stormont we
OL,15,Fproduce legislation that also deals
OL,16,Fwith the very harmful and dangerous
OL,17,Fpractices from the gambling industry."
