OL,4,Chelp available for gambling addition
OL,6,FDeclan Cregan is also in recovery. He
OL,7,Fnow delivers prevention sessions to
OL,8,Fstaff and players at sports clubs with
OL,9,Fthe charity Gambling with Lives.
OL,11,FHe said: "We encourage and we urge
OL,12,Fother sports clubs, youth groups,
OL,13,Fschools to get involved in the work
OL,14,Fthat we are doing, the education and
OL,15,Fawareness lessons that we provide to
OL,16,Fgive these young people the awareness.
OL,18,F"Then hopefully they will not go down
OL,19,Fthe road that I went down and
OL,20,Funfortunately many other people around
OL,21,Fme as well."
